              and humanity has been enslaved. Driven by logic and =
reason, the=20
              machines conquer entire galaxies with impunity. Yet, they =
live not=20
              in harmony. The very human desire for supremacy is alive =
and well=20
              among the machines, culminating every ten thousand years =
in the=20
              greatest contest the Universe has ever seen, a battle the =
machines=20
              call, "6.270".
              <P>The end of another ten thousand year cycle is nearly =
upon us.=20
